<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#MARMOR> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "MARMOR (Marine Advanced Geophysical Research Equipment and Mayotte Multidisciplinary Observatory for Research and Response) is an eight-year project funded by the ANR.\n\nThe MARMOR project has two objectives:\n\nto structure the French scientific community by providing the Epos-France research infrastructure (formerly Résif) with the equipment required to conduct high-level research using submarine seismology and geodesy tools,\n\nto establish an underwater observation infrastructure in Mayotte in order to ensure continuous, real-time, 24/7 seismological monitoring and to support multidisciplinary research on the phenomena associated with the ongoing seismo-volcanic crisis."@en .
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Virtuoso> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Un sistem open-source hibrid de gestionare a bazelor de date care oferă un depozit RDF, un endpoint SPARQL, o bază de date SQL și un server Linked Data."@ro .
